so collect information into your interaction with Havnor® Services and our website, for example, using embedded product technologies and cookies. We also obtain data from third parties.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color="custom" accent_color="#dcdcdc"][vc_custom_heading text="2. Information You Provide to Havnor Voluntarily" font_container="tag:h4|font_size:17px|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:27px" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1539089681678{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]1.1 When you subscribe to a newsletter, create an account, make a purchase or request information from Havnor, we will ask for things like contact, billing, shipping and communication information, payment card or financial account data, and account ID or credentials in order to fulfill your request. If you visit one of our stores or locations, attend a trade show or event, or otherwise contact us, you may also voluntarily provide similar information.

Interactive stories in some Havnor Services may allow you to invite friends, follow others, comment on or make unique posts, or share photos, video or other personal content. When you affirmatively share this content, we may collect and use it in accordance with this Notice. Additionally, by way of your social action, we may receive information about you from another user, such as when your friend posts content that includes you.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color="custom" accent_color="#dcdcdc"][vc_custom_heading text="3. Device and Product Operation" font_container="tag:h4|font_size:17px|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:27px" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1539089704101{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]1.1 If you download and use certain Havnor Service like software or an app, we may track and collect usage data, such as when the software or app accesses our servers, what information and files have been downloaded through the use of the software or app, and how you interact with the software or app during use. Some of this data may be protected as personal information under applicable data protection laws.

1.2 We collect this information to understand how you interact with Havnor® Services and provide you with the best experiences. We may also use this information for security purposes. We may associate the information we collect from more than one device that you use with other information that we have collected about you or your other devices.[/vc_column_text][hanor_simple_list simple_list_style="style-two" open_link="" simple_list_images="%5B%7B%22list_content%22%3A%22Geographic%20locations%2C%20such%20as%20through%20GPS%2C%20Bluetooth%2C%20or%20WiFi%20signals.%22%7D%2C%7B%22list_content%22%3A%22Connection%20information%20such%20as%20the%20name%20of%20your%20mobile%20operator%20or%20ISP%2C%20browser%20type%2C%20language%20and%20time%20zone%2C%20mobile%20phone%20number%20and%20IP%20address.%22%7D%2C%7B%22list_content%22%3A%22Communicate%20with%20you%20and%20others%20as%20part%20of%20our%20business.%22%7D%5D" bullet_color="#08b248" list_left="30px"][vc_separator color="custom" accent_color="#dcdcdc" css=".vc_custom_1536151437505{padding-top: 25px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="4. Information from Third Parties" font_container="tag:h4|font_size:17px|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:27px" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1538987043495{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]1.1 In some instances Havnor technology is used within a product or device that may collect personal information, which is not shared with Havnor. This information may be collected by the manufacturer of the product or device and you will need to read the privacy notice, privacy policy, or related terms published by that manufacturer to understand how they use your information.

